Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:37.12,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che bella espressione, mi eccita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.80,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Non resisto più!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:48.75,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nemmeno io!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:55.68,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.59,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bentornato, Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:22.09,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grazie... Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:24.84,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, non è nulla.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:31.60,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei Hiiragi, hai impegni per Domenica?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.91,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, sono libero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allora andiamo in città!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.78,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sì, andiamoci, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.06,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma che ti prende all'improvviso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.05,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,È in ritardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:51.50,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scusa per averti fatto aspettare!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come sto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:57.86,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cosa intendi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:01.06,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Con questi vestiti sembro più femminile, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.54,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beh, sì...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.18,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sei una ragazza dopotutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.40,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che succede così all'improvviso?
