Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.13,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.38,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Per oggi finiamo qui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:43.14,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professoressa Haruna, grazie del tuo lavoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.87,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sì, grazie anche a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.80,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che c'è? Non torni a casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.37,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vuoi forse darmi una lezione privata?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.61,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Figurati! Bene, ci vediamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:05.46,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non è accaduto nulla durante le ultime settimane, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.20,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che male!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.14,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.47,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, aspetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.66,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che crudele! Sorellona, questo per cos'era?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non ti avevo detto di non venire mai qui?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.64,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Però...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.73,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Torna a casa, subito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.97,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sbrigati, devi tornare a casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:42.64,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma di recente non ci sei mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:51.49,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace! Mi dispiace, Sakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.96,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma non puoi restare qui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.36,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Questa... Questa scuola è...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.01,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Troppo pericolosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.44,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ti prego! Farò qualsiasi cosa mi dirai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.58,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ma voglio rimanere insieme a te, anche solo per un altro giorno, sorellona!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Va bene allora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:19.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già, voglio proteggere il tuo sorriso.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.19,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si è suicidato in questa data,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:33.20,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ma aveva programmato nel dettaglio le lezioni anche per i giorni successivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.77,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki Yasuji non si è suicidato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.95,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aspetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.44,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiedo scusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:59.41,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor Tanemo, hai visto uno studente con un strana maschera correre qui intorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.57,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, non l'ho visto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.15,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capisco, grazie mille.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quel mascalzone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.32,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non potrò dormire sonni tranquilli finché non verrà preso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.91,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh professoressa Haruna, vai già a casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:25.48,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professoressa Haruna, tu conoscevi il professor Misaki che si è suicidato l'anno scorso, vero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.49,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? P-Perché me lo chiedi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:37.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ecco... Mi stavo chiedendo se avrei potuto salvarlo se fossi stata l'infermiera di questa scuola...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:44.34,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stavo leggendo il programma delle lezioni del professor Misaki, ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.20,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:51.30,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma più approfondisco la questione, e più sembra che non fosse intenzionato a suicidarsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.30,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Capisco...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:57.66,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ehm, com'era il professor Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.58,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Era un bravo insegnante.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.11,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gli piaceva insegnare ed era molto onesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:11.12,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assomigliava a Misawa Raika...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:17.68,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ehm, mi dispiace! Ora devo andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:21.02,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sì, scusa per averti trattenuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.28,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene. Ci vediamo, allora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.45,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Questa goduria! Non riesco ad averne abbastanza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:41.13,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, sbrigatevi! Noi stiamo aspettando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:47.48,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ogni giorno che passa sembra che ce ne siano sempre di più...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.59,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Fa' male, fa' male!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.15,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, non toglierlo dalla bocca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.14,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dovrò fare questo con tutti? Impossibile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:32.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perché le dissi una cosa del genere...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:42.53,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio fratello soffriva di vertigini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:48.91,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Una volta mi ha portata sulla ruota panoramica, durante un festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.96,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ma ha tenuto gli occhi chiusi tutto il tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.45,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, scusa! Non volevo annoiarti con questi discorsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:57.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figurati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.66,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.78,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:09.51,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perché non hai detto a nessuno della mia identità?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.22,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perché avrei dovuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.28,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, ecco, vedi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.48,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Una volta avevo una sorella maggiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.21,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Una volta avevi una sorella maggiore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:27.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi chiedo quanto tempo sia passato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si è suicidata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.16,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:36.78,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E per molto tempo non sono riuscito ad accettare che non ci fosse più.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:42.34,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi stavo chiedendo se tu ti stessi trovando in una situazione simile, ecco...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.90,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:49.10,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Se vuoi sapere la verità, continua a cercarla finché non ti riterrai soddisfatta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.98,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Altrimenti non sarai in grado di andare avanti, giusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.58,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.31,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prego.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.65,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non volevo dirglielo, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.72,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prego serviti pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.39,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sembra delizioso! Buon appetito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:39.90,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Mangiane quanto vuoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.05,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dove sta andando a quest'ora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:59.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\t(0,9960,\fs40.5)\fax-0.03\fay0.411\fnDFGGanShinKei-W7\bord0\c&H483A3D&\move(445.280,46,730,-40.5,0,9960)}Consiglio Studentesco
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.85,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finalmente domani è il giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.61,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già. Siamo pronti, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.99,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cosa dicono? Non riesco a sentire bene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.20,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sì, lascia fare a me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.60,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Questo è l'evento principale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.75,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Diamine, che presidente del consiglio studentesco astuto che sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:13.59,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lo faccio solo per far realizzare\N i desideri degli studenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.88,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già, sono sicuro che ne rimarranno estasiati.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:21.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E il mio rispetto nei tuoi confronti continua a crescere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I voti di tutti gli studenti della scuola stanno aumentando.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:30.04,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sembra che tutti si mettano  studiare se c'è in palio una succosa ricompensa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.54,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ricompensa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:38.03,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già, credo che nessuno studente possa chiedere una ricompensa migliore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.40,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misawa, stai bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.67,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sì...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.39,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sono stato io a dirle di cercare la verità finché non si sentisse soddisfatta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:05.72,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E ancora frequenta la scuola fingendosi un uomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.42,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deve aver incontrato qualche problema...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:12.06,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giusto! Perché non ci sono arrivato prima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.96,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non piangerò... col diavolo che lo farò!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.01,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi ero promessa che non avrei più pianto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.48,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che succede?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.07,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cosa stai facendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.93,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Esco per un po'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.52,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potrebbe passare del tempo prima del mio ritorno, non preoccuparti per me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V-Va bene...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.66,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma dove stai andando a quest'ora?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.24,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tieni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:47.89,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prendi queste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:52.59,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Con quelle chiavi potrai aprire la sala degli archivi ed ogni altra porta di questa scuola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.55,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ho un brutto presentimento...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.38,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forse dovrei tornare indietro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:12.01,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anche se oggi non c'è scuola, perché l'atmosfera è così tesa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quindi c'era davvero qualcuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.34,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma non è la dottoressa Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.43,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che importa, tanto le cattureremo tutte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.13,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:31.49,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perché...? Ho chiuso la porta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.33,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lei è...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non andare da solo! La atterreremo insieme!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.14,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.24,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lasciami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.73,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Col diavolo! Ora ti abbiamo presa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.11,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cosa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.73,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.15,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:14:59.81,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.16,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lasciatela!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.65,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liberatela!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:10.15,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vi prego! Lasciatela andare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Questa è colpa tua, professoressa Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.86,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Che hai detto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.22,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hai portato la tua sorellina nella sala insegnanti...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorellona, mi dispiace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,È tutta colpa mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.78,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sono venuta a scuola anche se mi avevi detto di non farlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.45,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuya! Lasciatela andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.87,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non mi importa cosa fate a me, ma...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che bella scenetta di amore fraterno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:45.01,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma tua sorella deve essere punita per essere entrata in questa scuola.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.92,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non fatelo! Lasciatela!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.47,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vi prego, non toccate Sakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:57.68,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ti offriremo un posto in prima fila, professoressa Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:02.75,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene, che ne dici se la puniamo sia davanti che dietro contemporaneamente?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.18,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già, bell'idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.75,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, voi! Osservate con attenzione!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.19,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,È raro poter assistere alla prima volta di una ragazza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.15,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!! Sorellona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.07,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorellona!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.69,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guarda, guarda. Che bella fichetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:27.56,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Falla vedere bene anche a tua sorella e agli altri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.86,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.48,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene, iniziamo il countdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.18,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cinque,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,quattro,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tre,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.92,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,due,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:54.99,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,uno,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.22,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:01.24,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.41,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Com'è stretta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.58,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Il mio cazzo si sta muovendo a scatti!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.08,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Una fica vergine è tutta un'altra cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:17.81,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Com'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:23.59,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{originale}Cosa si prova a perdere la verginità sia davanti che\N dietro contemporanemante, sotto\N gli occhi di tua sorella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:32.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene, che ne dici di venirle dentro alla sua prima volta, come abbiamo fatto anche a sua sorella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.44,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bell'idea! Mi piace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.50,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? N-No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.41,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.52,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, fa' male!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.31,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.99,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorellona, salvami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.07,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Salvami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:49.91,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:51.20,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,Perché ti rifiuti? I tuoi capezzoli sono così duri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.28,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:18:00.55,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fantastico! Stimolando i suoi capezzoli restringe ancora di più l'ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.31,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.60,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già, restringe anche la sua fica!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.66,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deve avere dei capezzoli molto sensibili.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.53,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.77,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene, che ne dici di venirle dentro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.62,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Già, è così stretta che non credo di poter resistere a lungo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.40,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene, veniamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forza, forza, forza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:39.10,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forza, forza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.25,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.97,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.22,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.27,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sto per venire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.54,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fantastico!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ora siamo al completo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:41.49,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Sakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.84,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E... eh? Cosa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.89,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene, che ne dite di iniziare l'evento principale?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:59.73,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fatevi avanti e divertitevi con le prede, fatene ciò che volete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:01.11,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Questa è la vostra ricompensa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.09,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.37,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,È fantastico dottoressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ho sempre desiderato scoparti,\N anche solo per una volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.31,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vale lo stesso per me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:15.17,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ho sempre fantasticato sul mettertelo nel culo in questo modo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Fantastico!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:23.47,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Degno di una ragazza appena sverginata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.42,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La tua fica è la migliore professoressa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.39,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La numero uno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.77,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorellona, salvami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:38.07,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuya... Mi dispiace, Sakuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:43.24,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai piangendo per la gioia di poter riassaggiare i nostri cazzi che non hai ricevuto per settimane?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:48.31,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dovrai farti tutti i qui presenti, quindi goditeli tutti!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.46,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, che ne pensi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.40,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che belle tette!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.31,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professoressa, prendilo tutto! Forza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.46,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,Professoressa... Professoressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forza, succhialo bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.33,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.98,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo! Sto per venire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.59,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.54,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sto per venirti in bocca, dottoressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:33.62,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professoressa, vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.25,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non è più vivace come prima, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.90,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forza, continua!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:02.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa' male! Smettila!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:06.74,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dai che ti piace. Prendilo, prendilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.38,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vedi? Che ti avevo detto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:13.55,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forza, rimettilo subito in bocca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:20.07,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che espressione! Sei così eccitante, dottoressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:23.36,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dottoressa! N-Non resisto più!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.84,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:26.14,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:30.64,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo anch'io!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:35.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professoressa... Professoressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:37.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Più veloce, più veloce!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:39.62,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sto per venire... Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sembra che si stia abituando in fretta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:47.47,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beh, dopotutto lei {\i1}è{\i0} la sorella della professoressa Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:49.16,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sono venuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.04,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Allora vengo anch'io!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:53.13,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:59.34,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dottoressa! Non mi basta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:02.56,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dottoressa Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.04,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:09.30,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anch'io! Vengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:14.46,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sto quasi per venire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:20.34,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vengo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:47.76,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Che bella vista...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:53.17,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Diamine, che studenti mezzi froci che abbiamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:57.54,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanno detto che sarebbero tornati appena avrebbero recuperato abbastanza sperma,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:59.95,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ma ancora non è tornato nessuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:05.19,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bastardo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.55,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, giusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:12.13,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ti avevo promesso di dirti qualcosa su Misaki Yasuji, vero?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:18.42,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ti dirò tutto, visto che ormai non potrai fare più nulla.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:20.81,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki Yasuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:23.56,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,è stato ucciso.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:28.46,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,È stato ucciso e solo {\i1}dopo{\i0} è\N stato buttato giù dal tetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.91,0:24:31.80,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E l'assassino, beh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:33.78,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sono io.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:38.38,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non ti avevo mai visto quell'espressione piena d'odio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:40.09,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.49,0:24:44.58,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi odi? E cosa hai intenzione di fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.40,0:24:47.71,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:49.97,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non ti perdonerò mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.84,0:24:55.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sfortunatamente non puoi fare nulla.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.63,0:25:01.65,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ormai l'unica cosa che puoi fare è diventare la nostra schiava sessuale per il resto della tua vita!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.65,0:25:03.60,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Razza di...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.93,0:25:09.17,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Puoi smettere di usare questa voce fastidiosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.11,0:25:10.98,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.74,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Professor Jounochii!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.31,0:25:19.28,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastardo! Chi sei?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:23.97,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ricordi quando una tua compagna di classe si suicidò, quando ancora andavi a scuola?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.45,0:25:25.75,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quando ancora andavo a scuola?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.14,0:25:27.98,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Di cosa stai parlando?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:33.12,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'è stata una tua compagna di classe che si è buttata dal tetto nel giorno del diploma, ricordi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.84,0:25:35.53,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giorno del diploma?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.71,0:25:39.69,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Io sono... suo fratello.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.64,0:25:44.86,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Fermati!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.59,0:25:48.24,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E {\i1}tu{\i0} ti sei mai fermato quando lei ti implorava di farlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.58,0:25:54.02,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non importa cosa ti dicesse, non l'hai ascoltata.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:26:00.07,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Per questo desidererei farti soffrire in eterno,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.52,0:26:03.67,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ma ringraziami che puoi morire senza dolore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.92,0:26:23.12,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'è n'è un altro. Non può essere lontano...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.86,0:26:25.78,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.78,0:26:26.43,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attento!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:34.36,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Professor Tanemo...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.54,0:26:38.02,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.20,0:26:44.92,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Salvatemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:46.67,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Salvatemi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.23,0:26:50.29,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quante volte avrai sentito questa parola prima d'ora?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.42,0:26:56.73,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:05.53,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avanzo di una maledizione...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.51,0:27:11.04,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Io... Io non morirò!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.51,0:27:15.15,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voglio possedere ogni cosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.15,0:27:19.16,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ecco perché Yasuji doveva sparire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.11,0:27:21.37,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossibile!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.37,0:27:24.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avevo messo gli occhi sulla professoressa Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:29.50,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma quel dannato Yasuji mi rubava tutto ciò che mi apparteneva!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.23,0:27:37.16,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ecco perché ho chiesto aiuto al professore!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.75,0:27:40.17,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Come osi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.46,0:27:45.97,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Se devo morire, allora facciamolo insieme, professoressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.97,0:27:48.64,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Muori con me, professoressa Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:51.83,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorellona...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.21,0:27:54.36,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok?! Haruna...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.17,0:27:59.19,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.19,0:28:00.27,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.16,0:28:17.92,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Devo vivere...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.54,0:28:20.16,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ho promesso...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.95,0:28:23.56,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ho promesso che avrei vissuto anche per lui...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:27.95,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non posso morire...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.47,0:28:29.93,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Questo è ciò che Yasuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.56,0:28:32.39,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio fratello?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.74,0:28:38.26,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuji mi ha detto che dovevo vivere.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.36,0:28:41.13,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professoressa Haruna...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.63,0:28:48.45,Wa wana Dialogue top,,0,0,0,,Sono entrato in questa scuola perché secondo le informazioni che ho trovato, i due tizi che hanno costretto mia sorella al suicidio si trovavano qui...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.50,0:28:52.41,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ed ho sempre investigato sin da allora.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.06,0:28:54.01,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.01,0:28:56.80,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avevano falsificato i loro nomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.80,0:28:59.93,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chi pensavano di ingannare con un tranello così semplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.03,0:29:04.01,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Volevo farti avere la tua vendetta, ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.02,0:29:06.36,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:13.99,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace di averti fatto vedere tutto questo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.92,0:29:17.70,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Non mi importa se ti dimentichi di me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.26,0:29:25.20,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anzi, dovresti dimenticare subito tutta questa faccenda e andartene da questa scuola.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.46,0:29:28.23,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi-Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.81,0:29:31.12,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allora addio.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.26,0:29:35.22,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.88,0:29:40.63,Wa wana Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No!!
